headline.print_headline: Police Arrest Second Man in Portland Shooting
headline.main: Police Arrest Second Man in Portland Shooting

lead_paragraph: An 18-year-old man arrested Sunday is the second of three people believed to be involved in a shooting outside an alternative Portland high school, police said.
